	"description": "Async and await might sound complicated...but they&#x27;re as easy as pizza pie once\nyou dive in.\n\nWe all use async and await in our daily routines.\n\nWhat is an async task?\nAn async task lets you complete other tasks while the async task is still\nworking towards completion.\n\nHere are some day-to-day async task examples\nExample 1:\nYou order food at a drive-thru which starts your food request (an async task).\n\nYou pull forward in the drive-thru line (the next task), while your food is\nprepared.\n\nYou di",
